    "F 0 values are averaged over every input symbol using the extracted durations d (Figure 3).",
    "Unvoiced values are excluded from the calculation.",
    "For training, the values are standardized to mean of 0 and standard deviation of 1.",
    "If there are no voiced F 0 estimates for a particular symbol, its pitch is being set to 0.",
    "We have not seen any improvements from modeling F 0 in log-domain.Following [5], we tried averaging to three pitch values per every symbol, in the hope to capture the beginning, middle and ending pitch for every symbol."
